'''EconSimp''' is a [[Bioeconomics (fisheries)|bioeconomic]] [[fisheries management|management]] [[model (abstract)|model]] of the [[Barents Sea]] [[fisheries]]. It consists of two modules modelling respectively the Barents Sea [[ecosystem]] and the [[Norway|Norwegian]] [[fishing fleet|fleet]] structure and activity. The ecosystem module is the multispecies model [[Aggmult]] developed at the [[Norwegian Institute of Marine Research]] and the fleet module is [[EconMult]].

